RELEASE NOTES for BANDIT
========================

This is the release "1.7.0" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

See https://docs.phyglos.org/bandit for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES
=============

* Reordered timestamp position in names of log files
* Added actions to move, rename, delete, etc. bundles
* Refactored code to work with systems
  * Removed bespoke command "bandit-builder-enter" and "bandit-target-enter"
  * Added bandit actions: "bandit -s builder enter" and "bandit -s target enter"
* Cleaned up old code and sanitized hard tabs
* Removed unnecessary exports for variables and functions
* Added variable BUILD_CATALOG


